parameters: Takumi: "You called me here, what do you want?"
Takumi: "Is the old man behind also a guest?"
Karen: "He's not involved. Don't mind him."

Takumi: "But man, this is one hell of a room. It amazes me every time
I come here."

Takumi: "Going to the trouble of calling me out, are you hoping for a
reconciliation?"
Karen: "You sold our sex tape to a publisher, didn't you!"
Takumi: "Sorry about that, I was a bit strapped for cash."
Karen: "I gave you more than enough money to get sick of it!"

Karen: "How many hours do you think I've been waiting? You're always
so loose with time."
Takumi: "Sorry, sorry, I was meeting with Morisaki."

Karen: "That's exactly who I wanted to talk about when I called you
here!"
Karen: "I'll get straight to the point."

Karen: "I want you to thoroughly destroy the relationship between
Morisaki and Amasawa."
Takumi: "You haven't changed a bit. Still as arrogant as ever."

Karen: "What's the matter, you're good at this sort of thing, aren't
you? If you like Morisaki, then Amasawa is in your way, right?"

Takumi: "From what I can tell, those two are head over heels for each
other."
Karen: "I know that without you telling me!"

Takumi: "Even for me, it's going to take some time to bring down
Morisaki. Well, I'm currently working on that..."
Karen: "Then the conversation should be quick."
Takumi: "This is... Are you that close with Amasawa?"
Karen: "No, Amasawa rejected me. So I kissed him by force."

Karen: "I am Saionji Karen. Is there anything wrong with doing as I
please?"
Takumi: "Your ruthlessness is just like mine."
Takumi: "So, Morisaki is mine, and you'll take Amasawa?"
Karen: "No, I don't care about Amasawa anymore."

Karen: "I realized after talking to him. He will never be swayed by
me..."
Karen: "So I thought, why not completely break him."
Takumi: "Hahaha! You really are a terrible woman."
Takumi: "Well, leave it to me. As your ex, I'll lend a hand."

Karen: "I appreciate it. Show that photo to Morisaki right away. I
can't wait to see the look on her face."
Takumi: "Well, don't rush. This is our last resort."

Takumi: "I'll use it if I decide that I can't bring her down with my
own abilities."

Takumi: "And when that time comes, I'll need a little cooperation from
you."

Karen: "But make sure you separate those two for good. If you fail,
I'll crush you with all my might."
Takumi: "Yes, yes, leave it to me, Lady Karen."
